# The daemon staged for packaging: a copy of dist/ plus ~78MB of production
# node_modules, rebuilt by `npm run stage` on every `npm run dist`. Output, not
# source. (The icons next to it under desktop/build/ ARE source — hence the
# narrow path rather than desktop/build/.)
desktop/build/daemon/

